                            <h3 class="text-warning">Utilities Suppliers</h3>
                            <p>You should always ensure that your heating and electicity suppliers know if you're disabled, vulnerable, or on dialysis. You will be placed onto a certain list which means they will make sure to contact you prior to any disruption to service and help ensure your electricity is not interupted if you need it for medical care.</p>
