                            <h3 class="text-purple">Clinic Counsellors</h3>
                            <p>Many renal clinics have a counsellor or counselling team. These professionals have extensive mental health experience as well as an intimate knowledge of CKD and the challenges which come associated with it.</p>
                        </div>
