                            <i class="fa fa-facebook-official" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="media-body">
                            <h3 class="text-info">Chronic Kidney Disease UK on Facebook</h3>
                            <p>There are various Facebook groups available, howevever you should definitely join <a class="text-body" target="blank" href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/1444648835635226" aria-hidden="true">Chronic Kidney Disease UK</a>, it is a huge network of CKD warriors and carers.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>


                <!-- Media -->
                <div class="col-sm-6 col-lg-6 col-xs-12">
                    <div class="media mb-6">
                        <div class="media-icon-large bg-info mr-xl-4">
                            <i class="fa fa-facebook-official" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="media-body">
                            <h3 class="text-info">KDARS for Kids on Facebook</h3>
                            <p>If you are caring for a child who has CKD then you should consider joining <a class="text-body" target="blank" href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/750940214926395" aria-hidden="true">KDARS for Kids</a>, to discuss supporting children with CKD.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>


